tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE project_tracking (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    time_spent DECIMAL(10,2),
    budget DECIMAL(10,2),
    client_feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  time_spent FLOAT,
  budget_allocation DECIMAL(10,2),
  client_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE client_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  feedback TEXT,
  satisfaction_rating INT,
  feedback_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Project (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  project_budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
  client_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE TimeTracking (
  tracking_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  employee_id INT,
  hours_worked DECIMAL(5, 2),
  date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE projects (
 project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 start_date DATE,
 end_date DATE,
 budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
 client_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE time_tracking (
 time_entry_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 project_id INT,
 employee_id INT,
 time_spent DECIMAL(5,2),
 date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE budget_allocation (
 allocation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 project_id INT,
 expense_type VARCHAR(255),
 amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
 date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE client_feedback (
 feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 project_id INT,
 client_name VARCHAR(255),
 feedback_text TEXT,
 rating INT
);
